title: BBQ Blitz S01E01 Little Rock Wrangle PDTV.x264-JIVE.mp4
description:
Game on! Food Network Star winner and former NFL player Eddie Jackson is taking a barbecue battle on the road in BBQ Blitz. In each city, three of the best grillers, smokers, and fire-roasters will cook off for a chance to win $5,000 and the title of best barbecue chef.




BBQ Blitz - Season 1, Episode 1



Little Rock Wrangle

Food Network Star winner Eddie Jackson makes his way back to where he played college football in Little Rock, Ark. to check out what the top chefs in town can do in the BBQ Blitz arena! Special judges, chef Kardea Brown and former football player Anthony Lucas, will help deem the BBQ Blitz Champ and award the $5,000 prize.



Original Air Date: 09-Oct-2015
